to siberia 
if i had to make the decision right now id say id never be 
interested in going to washington he said my impression is 
that people dont enjoy those jobs anymore they have to spend half 
their time in useless activity and a lot of whats left over is 
directed toward raising money 
cowper 50 moved to alaska in 1968 but still speaks with the 
